  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to evaluate if there is an association between platelet inhibition
      and surgery-related bleeding in patients undergoing emergent cardiac surgery during dual
      antiplatelet therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Blood for measuring platelet function is drawn before induction of anesthesia
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
